Package: linux-image-4.14-254-xiaomi-miatoll
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel for Xiaomi Miatoll
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Xiaomi Miatoll device.
 .
 Note: This package only ships the kernel image and modules, you should probably
 look at the linux-bootimage-4.14-254-xiaomi-miatoll package for a bootimage suitable
 for Android boot loaders.

Package: linux-bootimage-4.14-254-xiaomi-miatoll
Architecture: arm64
Pre-Depends: flash-bootimage (>= 4)
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         linux-image-4.14-254-xiaomi-miatoll (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Linux kernel for Xiaomi Miatoll - Android Boot Image
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Xiaomi Miatoll device.
 .
 Note: This package ships an Android Boot Image bundled with Halium's
 initramfs.

Package: linux-headers-4.14-254-xiaomi-miatoll
Architecture: arm64
